OL,3,CEx-soldier jailed for social media
OL,4,Cposts inciting racial hatred
OL,6,FA former soldier who made Facebook
OL,7,Fposts referring to "civil war" in the
OL,8,Faftermath of the Southport attacks has
OL,9,Fbeen jailed for two years.
OL,11,FDaffron Williams, 40, who served on
OL,12,Ftours of Afghanistan and Iraq,
OL,13,Fpreviously pleaded guilty to a charge
OL,14,Fof publishing material likely to stir
OL,15,Fup racial hatred relating to public
OL,16,Fposts made between 19 July and 11
OL,17,FAugust.
