OL,4,Cposts inciting racial hatred
OL,6,FCardiff Crown Court heard the posts,
OL,7,Fmade before and after three girls were
OL,8,Ffatally stabbed at a dance class on 29
OL,9,FJuly, included Williams describing
OL,10,FTommy Robinson, real name Stephen
OL,11,FYaxley-Lennon, as a "f***ing hero".
OL,13,FIn one post, the day after the
OL,14,Fincident in Southport, Williams wrote:
OL,15,F"Civil war is here. The only thing
OL,16,Fthat's missing is bullets. That's the
OL,17,Fnext step."
