OL,6,FThe court heard Williams, of
OL,7,FTonypandy, south Wales, has been
OL,8,Fdiagnosed with post-traumatic stress
OL,9,Fdisorder (PTSD) relating to his time
OL,10,Fin the army, during which he served in
OL,11,FAfghanistan and Iraq.
OL,13,FTracey Lloyd-Clarke, the Recorder of
OL,14,FCardiff, told Williams that there had
OL,15,Fbeen "serious public disorder"
OL,16,Ffollowing the Southport attacks.
OL,18,FShe said: "It was on 31 July this year
OL,19,Fthat South Wales Police received
OL,20,Fcomplaints about your Facebook account.
