OL,6,F"Your Facebook profile was an open
OL,7,Fprofile, which means any member of the
OL,8,Fpublic, anywhere in the country and
OL,9,Fthe world, could view your profile and
OL,10,Fsee your comments."
OL,12,FThe judge said Williams had posted a
OL,13,Fnumber of "racist comments" before the
OL,14,FSouthport incident and the disorder
OL,15,Fthat followed.
OL,17,FSignificant comments included Williams
OL,18,Fposting "Let's just do something FFS"
OL,19,Fand "Civil war is here, the only thing
OL,20,Fthat's missing is bullets, that's the
OL,21,Fnext step", she said.
