OL,4,Cposts inciting racial hatred
OL,6,FWilliams was arrested on 11 August and
OL,7,Fapologised when shown the Facebook
OL,8,Fposts, which he told police he
OL,9,Fregretted, the court heard.
OL,11,FConsidering evidence about Williams'
OL,12,FPTSD, the judge said it was a
OL,13,Fmitigating factor for sentence, but
OL,14,Fadded: "You knew exactly what you were
OL,15,Fdoing, your posts were intentional."
OL,17,FReferences submitted to the court on
OL,18,FWilliams' behalf made clear he served
OL,19,Fhis community as well as his country
OL,20,Fand had organised charity events.
