OL,6,FJudge Lloyd-Clarke added: "I accept
OL,7,Fyou have strong personal mitigation
OL,8,Fbut given your encouragement to others
OL,9,Fto act ` your references to civil war
OL,10,Fand to bullets ` I am satisfied this
OL,11,Foffending is so serious that only
OL,12,Fcustody is sufficient."
OL,14,FProsecuting, Alex Orndal said Williams
OL,15,Fhad pleaded guilty to the charge
OL,16,Fagainst him when he appeared before
OL,17,FCardiff Magistrates' Court in August
OL,18,Fand had been in custody since then.
