OL,6,FIn one Facebook comment, Williams
OL,7,Fsaid: "I am racist as f***, only to
OL,8,Fthose who sap the life out of society
OL,9,Fand disrespect culture. Our future as
OL,10,FBritish is so uncertain it is unreal."
OL,12,FOn 24 July, he wrote: "Come on guys,
OL,13,Fit is time to stand up. Everything our
OL,14,Fancestors, grandparents and parents
OL,15,Ffought for is ruined. Let's do
OL,16,Fsomething."
OL,18,FFour days later, Williams posted
OL,19,Fimages from a Tommy Robinson rally in
OL,20,FLondon, which he attended on 27 July.
