OL,6,FHe wrote: "If that level of support
OL,7,Fcontinues, we will win our freedom
OL,8,Fback. That was too big to be called a
OL,9,Fracist protest."
OL,11,FWilliams added: "I have seen today
OL,12,Fthey are trying to put Tommy Robinson
OL,13,Fin jail. God bless Tommy Robinson,
OL,14,Ff***ing hero."
OL,16,FMr Orndal told the court how Williams
OL,17,Falso posted two AI generated images
OL,18,Ffollowing the Southport incident.
